<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230019>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Anharpyrhynchus spp, female. Anharpyrhynchus elizae sp. nov. (A-C from type host, D—from Colaptes auratus), A—palp in dorsal view; B—leg I in ventral view; C—leg II in ventral view; D—palpalae in dorsal view. Anharpyrhynchus monstrosus (Fritsch) (E and F): E—palpalae in dorsal view (from Corvus monedula); F—palpalae in dorsal view (from Corvus glandarius)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230019/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

